headline: Why Southwest Airlines Lost Altitude Today
summary: A day earlier, United Airlines Holdings said it was seeing a "stable" revenue and booking environment heading into the busy summer travel season.  Is Southwest Airlines a buy?  Investors shouldn't make too much of the Southwest/United comparison, as they were slightly different questions, but Southwest could indeed be a standout to the downside.
